[SPEAKER_08]: I sit currently under the vacant properties we do for residential.

890
01:34:40,035 --> 01:34:52,238
[SPEAKER_08]: We do require a local agent and that usually comes to the 24 hour emergency phone number that we have been able to call as well as the owner who may be a very far away distant entity.

891
01:34:52,319 --> 01:34:59,761
[SPEAKER_08]: So we do typically require that and increasingly we ask for copies of home of property owners

