1172
02:04:30,583 --> 02:04:47,935
[SPEAKER_13]: When I talked to Kayla most recently, I think the point that she made to me was that she was really happy that we had emphasized this idea of enforcement discretion and still leaving open channels of communications with

1173
02:04:49,233 --> 02:04:57,556
[SPEAKER_13]: with property owners that might comply with the city or might want to work with the city and to avoid fees that way.

1174
02:04:58,076 --> 02:05:11,641
[SPEAKER_13]: And so she had told me that in her conversations with staff, people would feel better about the ordinance if there was a section in here that just made it more clear that discretion was possible.

1175
02:05:12,581 --> 02:05:16,743
[SPEAKER_13]: And so this draft language is speaking to that.

1176
02:05:19,717 --> 02:05:20,097
[SPEAKER_12]: Thank you.

